data.description: Beautifully remodeled 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom solar home with an attached bonus/hobby room that has been used as a 5th bedroom in the past! Over 1800 sq. ft. with an updated kitchen, updated windows, all new plumbing, updated electrical panel, newer heater, newer ceiling fans and custom blinds! Large 9800 sq. ft. lot with big workshop/storage shed in the backyard, double & single gates out to the alley & a large covered carport that leads onto the uncovered patio in the back! A truly unique gem!
